  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Released in Japan as \"Magical Drop III + Wonderful\" and in Europe simply as \"Magical Drop III\", this version packages Magical Drop III: Yokubari Tokudaigou! with a console port of Magical Drop Plus 1!\n\nThe game features a slightly slower gameplay pace than the Japanese version, omits the \"Arcade\" version and gallery from the Japanese release, and translates the game's script into multiple languages. Unlike previous versions released outside of Japan, this game retains the Japanese voice work; similarly, the port of Magical Drop Plus 1! is based on the Japanese version instead of Chain Reaction.",
